text: Selenge Kimoto (born 15 August 1966) is cyclist from the Democratic Republic of the Congo. He competed in the individual road race at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Democratic Republic of the Congo male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of the Democratic Republic of the Congo Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
